# Lao Text Evaluation ğŸ§ªğŸ‡±ğŸ‡¦

**Grapheme-aware evaluation toolkit** for Lao OCR or text models â€” including CER, WER, character-level error breakdowns, and alignment visualizations.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- âœ… Character Error Rate (CER) and Word Error Rate (WER)
- âœ… Grapheme-level alignment using Unicode-aware splitting
- âœ… Lao-specific character classification: consonants, vowels, tone marks
- âœ… Visual alignment plots (color-coded matches, insertions, deletions, substitutions)
- âœ… CLI interface for single or batch file comparison
- âœ… Export results to CSV
- âœ… Generate sample data for quick testing

